 lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">家，成立分公司</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">家，壮实集团规模，完成新四版上市，融资</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">亿，广告招商收入</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">亿计，同时启动并开发海外市场，为集团进入创业板上市铺平道路</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">公司秉承以人为本，服务社会，回报客户的经营理念，将广告招商收入的</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">50%</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">加权平分给终端消费客户（以广告点击积分为依据），</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">10%</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">作为慈善基金，</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">20%</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">作为市场流通费用，</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">20%</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">作为公司发展基金，当公司成功上市时，公司将给高管、市场总监、市场经理，市场主管、分销商、代理商配送原始股票</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">创业艰辛苦难言，无限商机在眼前，让我们用热情的双手，诚挚地欢迎天下有识之士加盟</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">零乐购</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt;\">，共铸我们更加美好的未来</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','4','1','1403569761');
INSERT INTO ecm_article ( `article_id`, `code`, `title`, `cate_id`, `store_id`, `link`, `content`, `sort_order`, `if_show`, `add_time` ) VALUES  ('44','','常见问题','35','0','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">问：零乐购到底想干什么？老是这样送东西图什么呢？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;答：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">零乐购想打造一个网上平台，它采取的推广模式就是拿东西换人气，换点击率。就像电视台拼命播好看的节目大家随便免费看，为的是收视率，收视率高了就会出现广告商。互联网的计算公式就</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">是点击率</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">财富。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">问：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">公司老是这样免费换商品，资金是否会断链？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">大家有这样的疑问是因为有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">个误区：</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">以为一直是由零乐购支付商品</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">以为积分只能用于购物</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">以为不花钱就是白拿，产品拿了就走</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">：那么老百姓之所以有第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">个疑问是因为我们之前接触的生意或消费方式，都是以买卖双方关系存在的，大家以为如果卖方不收钱了，这个商家一定坚持不了多久，但是在互联网的世界里是不同的，是有第三方买单的：比如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">360</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、百度等都是有第三方买单的。但是第三方买单的前提是：这个网站要有点击率。所以零乐购先用东西换人气，人气高了也会有厂商出现。因此前期平台上的东西是零乐购提供的，后期点击流量达到一定量时，会由广告商提供，其实零乐购目的就是要打造一个帮广告商发放商品来提高知名度的平台。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">：积分除了购物外还可以用于注册。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">：老百姓不是通常意义上的白拿，只是用浏览网站跟公司做了交换而已。但老百姓认为，只要买东西不花钱就意味着免费，没有零乐购大家也要上网，上网同时顺便浏览网站就可以得积分换购产品。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">问：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">积分的来源于哪里？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;答：</span>1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">以货换分：可将滞销产品换成积分，或进货换分赚差价。例如：您在某公司进</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万元货，某公司会给您一定的销售奖励，假如您不是零乐购会员，您就只拿这一次奖励，接下来您得把货物销售出去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">，而且销售面很窄，效率很低；现在您可以把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万元产品放到零乐购网上商城平台，营业面迅速扩大到全国，换成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万积分（因为市面上的产品最高是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">折），当您用于注册的时候，是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1:1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">变现，变现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万元。您只进了一次货，换个方式卖</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">却拿了两次利润。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">到实体店收分：例如：理发店理一个发要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元，您可以跟老板谈，预付</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">次共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元，老板一定不会拒绝，然后让我们的会员用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">积分理一次发，相当于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">折收到了积分。而且在您分享新用户的时候，新用户觉得积分用途很多，甚至可以去理发，提高成交率。而您没有给理发店投资装修、出租一分钱，这些实体店却成为了您的旗舰店。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">问：</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">公司的利润在哪里？</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;答：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">零乐购平台有人气以后，公司的利润点会非常多，因为在互联网上</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">流量</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">=</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">财富</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">比如说：广告、平台使用费、购物佣金等等。零乐购只要拥有了用户量，一定就是赢家！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">问：</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">零乐购公司是否会不长久？（导致公司不长久的原因可一一排除）。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; 答：</span>1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">资金链断裂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">公司后期产品由第三方支付，可永续发展</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">公司卷钱逃跑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">------</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">大多数公司资金走向是上行，非正规公司有卷钱的机会，而零乐购资金走向下行，公司无钱可卷。（一&middot;消费者通过支付宝把钱给商家是一手给钱一手给货，第三方支付平台，安全可靠，</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">二&middot;商家在自己网店赚区自己合法利润，合情合理合法）</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、传销</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">构成传销的最基本条件是多层次团队计酬，零乐购不具备。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">、违法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">零乐购的经营根本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">是购物、分销、代理、转销售、易货和积分换购产品</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">，融合B2B、B2C、C2C、020等先进网购模式，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">而这些模式的诞生并非零乐购原创。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">比如：商场搞活动时，买了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1680</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元产品，商场返</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元代金券，代金券花完就没有了，在零乐购平台您同样是购买了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1680</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元的产品，公司同样返给您代金券，只不过是以账号的形式支付的，这个账号可以源源不断的每个月产生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">代金券。同样是消费得代金券，只不过零乐购的力度大一些而已。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">问：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">公司不给现金，一年到头都是积分，我不愿意干？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">答：</span>如果一年到头都是积分，说明您没有任何销售。那么在其他公司，产品特别棒，待遇非常好，但是如果您没有销售，到年底的时候，公司会给您什么呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">年呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">！</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">再看零乐购平台，您一年到头同样没有销售，零乐购是没给您钱，但是给了您</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7200~25200</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">积分换购产品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">年呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">~25.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">万积分换购产品！</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">在其他公司是给您提成佣金，前提是您得先给公司做业绩。零乐购也给奖金，经销商所有的利润都来自于市场的销售业绩！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">问：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">为什么把我的产品（比如：鞋子）变积分？</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">积分又不是钱？或者变一堆积分有什么用？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">答</span>1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">因为对于消费者来说，鞋子的触点面很窄，如果没有需求，就会影响成交率。把鞋子换成积分，您的触点面积就会扩大而且是消费者今后免费获得的理念，加大成交率。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">例如：你开了鞋店，鞋子不好卖，你发现隔壁超市的生意好，你就想开超市，超市里有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">千款商品，你就得进</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">千款商品才能经营，也就是说，你想卖什么货，您都得要先进什么货，但是在零乐购网上商城平台里就不用您再扩大投资了，您把部分鞋子换成积分，然后在给别人注册时，您展示的不再只是单一的鞋子了，您一定会说，李姐，您如果注册了这个账号，不但可以用积分换我的鞋子，还可以换化妆品用，换保健品吃，换日常用品等。。。。。。。，李姐原本不想买鞋子，但是她想用护肤品，而且今后可以免费享用，所以加大了成交的概率。您没有直接卖鞋，但您同样把鞋子换成了钱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">鞋子分</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">变</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">------</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">钱</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;答</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">您还是那个开鞋店的，你想买一套护肤品用或是保健品吃，如果没有零乐购，您是不能用鞋子购买化妆品或保健品的，那么现在，您把鞋子换成积分，直接拿积分购买护肤品、日常用品用或保健品就可以了！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">鞋子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">变</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-------</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">护肤品</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">您缺多少积分就换多少相应数量的鞋子，其余的鞋子还是照旧卖，现金流是不变的。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">问：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">零乐购的核心是什么？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;答：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">零乐购的核心是有偿关注，老百姓看电视剧、上网看新闻都是免费的，其实无意识的在给这些媒体无偿捐献了关注度，这些媒体依靠这些收视率和点击率，形成了巨大的注意力经济，媒体是赚了，但没人给老百姓一分利润；在零乐购平台，同样是依靠老百姓的关注度，但是零乐购取之于民，还之于民，根据老百姓关注的时间给予实物回报。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\"></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">问：零乐购公司的利润点和其他公司利润点有何不同？</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;答：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">大多数公司的利润点都在一个点上：比如卖保健品，无论采取什么销售模式，利润点都在保健品上，现在您就是保健品公司老板，我是经销商，一瓶保健品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">150</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元，现在我卖掉了一瓶，接下来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">----- </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">要给我提成，也就是分利润给我，俗称利润分配，也就是分钱，谁跟谁分钱呢？是老板和经销商分钱，那么利润分配的规则是谁制定的呢？一定是老板制定的，美其名曰奖金制度，经销商是遵守游戏规则的，是被动的。大家都要分这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">150</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元钱，利润点在一个点上，也就是说，老板的利润和经销商的利润是一对矛盾体，是不可调和的矛盾体，而作为经销商又占弱势，所以经销商的钱被沉淀是正常的。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">那么在零乐购这个平台，大家有没有发现，我们的利润点就不在一个点上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">----</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">经销商赚的是市场推广的钱，公司的利润是平台使用费啊、广告等等，经销商要钱，公司要人气，每当您赚了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">元的时候，公司多了一个用户，老百姓要东西，公司要流量，是各取所需，公司与经销商不但不是矛盾体，反而是相依为命、唇齿相依的关系。所以在零乐购，你不再是被动的由公司给你发工资，公司也不屑于设什么沉淀啊陷阱啊来考核你，大家的利润来自于市场业绩，有多大的本事尽情发挥！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"