one; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3.如您在下订单时选择了\"需要发票\"，请仔细检查发票是否随商品一起送到，如未收 到发票，请与零乐购网店客服中心联系。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 30px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 30px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">特别提醒：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1.您在收货验货时需第三方物流的视线范围内，打开零乐购自有配送包装，不在第三 方物流视线范围内验收商品，出现问题，即不予办理退货、补货 。零乐购在此提醒您务必认真清点商品！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: transparent; list-style-type: none; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #666666; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-decoration: none; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2.有个别配送商是要求先付款才能打开包装箱的，在这种情况下，请您检查外包装。 如外包装有破损，请在发货单上注明。</span></p>','4','1','1403574662');
INSERT INTO ecm_article ( `article_id`, `code`, `title`, `cate_id`, `store_id`, `link`, `content`, `sort_order`, `if_show`, `add_time` ) VALUES  ('49','','企业理念','38','0','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌模式：零乐购是以互联网</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">B2B</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">B2C</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">O2O</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">为平台，将电子商务与超市，物流等用为一体的立体商务模式，充分体现消费就业，消费养老，消费投资，消费分红的先进理念。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌优势：让虚拟与实体亲密融合，减少中间环节加速商品流通，提供最具价值的消费及前卫的投资理念，创建最先进的立体商业模式，打造中国最完善的商业体系，彰显魅力的零乐购</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌主张：省钱</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">省力</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">省时</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">省心</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌格局：爱国爱家爱商城</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">兴业兴邦中华</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌使命：品牌人才事业</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">责任</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">荣誉</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">国家</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌愿景：颠覆传统商业模式</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">打造新型商业帝国</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">品牌保障：零乐购不赚取商品的利润，其它网上商城即使廉价，但一个共性最终还是要赚取利润，零乐购的颠覆就是零利润。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购设立企业和产品入住机构，为消费者把好第一关，区别于其它网上商城，只要申请，缴纳费用，即可入驻，零乐购严格的准入制，确保了消费者的利益。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">企业价值观：社会的认可，是企业生存和发展的前提，社会价值是企业的最高价值。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">企业目标：一卓越的产品品质，超群的管理水平，优异的市场业绩，规范的行业标准，建立零乐购物国界的霸主品牌，独领世界电子商务之风骚，一展中国民族品牌之风采</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">企业宗旨：创新消费文化，造福社会大众</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">企业意愿：减少流通环节，瓦解利益垄断，增加就业渠道</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">这是一个百年不遇的合作商机，零乐购</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">商机无限</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：是电子商务与线下超市的完美结合的平台</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：初建期间免除一切上架费，柜台费，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">DM</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">费，条码费等</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：万国物连的雏形，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">年预计达到</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">家以上</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：线下超市是电子商务的提货中心，为会员提高多维度服务</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：采取积分和现金相结合，大部分网络积分都会到超市进行消费</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：超市占地约</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.5&mdash;3</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">万平米，卖场占地约</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.8-2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">万平米，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：超市采取平价制，大部分产品公司将舍去一部分利润，用于促销和积分配比，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">零乐购：适合网上销售的产品可申请本公司网络上架，价格双方协定</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">声明，为防止假冒伪劣产品，保护国家品牌商和消费者之利益，零乐购仅接受商品品牌商合作。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: mceinline;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','3','1','1403574703');
