spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">甲壳素具有如下特点：<br /><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: simsun; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">、甲壳素是糖类中唯一的碱性多糖。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 13.45pt 0cm; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: simsun; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">、甲壳素资源也是自然界中唯一的含氮量最高的天然资源。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 13.45pt 0cm; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: simsun; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #38761d; font-size: 13.5pt;\">、甲壳素是世人类迄今为止发现唯一天然的带阳离子基团的可食性动物纤维。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 13.45pt 0cm; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"